Woody, could we have            
some more pretzels, please?     

00:09.175 --> 00:10.843
                     Woody?     

00:12.012 --> 00:13.445
     Oh, sorry, Dr. Crane.      

00:13.513 --> 00:16.047
    I... I was just thinking    
 about how big the universe is. 

00:17.117 --> 00:18.283
              Yes, it is, Woody.

00:18.351 --> 00:19.351
            As a matter of fact,

00:19.419 --> 00:20.519
                  it's expanding
                all the time.   

00:20.587 --> 00:22.521
     Spiraling outward,         
     ad infinitum,              

00:22.589 --> 00:23.922
     from the center            
     of its origin              

00:23.990 --> 00:26.692
